{"tid":1180110,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【引渡惡法】不滿李家超「老屈」法律界唔了解修例 選委陳景生向林鄭下戰書","createTime":"2019-05-31T14:44:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T02:20:48.000Z","uid":255427,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b25fcebba5ba59e63745c1fc7a119a780bc3f0ea","tid":1180110,"uid":255427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T14:44:50.000Z","msg":"特區政府無視社會強烈反對聲音，企硬修訂《逃犯條例》，保安局局長李家超今日出席立法會保安事務委員會特別會議時，更「老屈」新聞界及法律界人士不了解修例內容。繼香港記者協會發聲明反駁，30名法律界選委更向特首林鄭月娥下「戰書」，邀作公開會面，討論修訂《逃犯條例》及修例對一國兩制的影響。<br />\n代表30名法律界選委、大律師公會前主席陳景生致涵林鄭月娥的信件指出，鑑於保安局局長李家超今日在立法會的言論，故邀請特首或相關官員於下月12日或之前，出席公開會面，以解釋當局所指法律界不明白修例的地方，也藉此機會討論修訂《逃犯條例》的利與弊，以及對本港法治及一國兩制的影響。"},{"pid":"a2e08ae4b9633827ac5574a19ba07526f1c6f1cb","tid":1180110,"uid":160605,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T14:57:20.000Z","msg":"777點會理你<br />\n全世界都有反對聲音理你呢幾十位 2打6?"},{"pid":"72169df5d0ee1198d3c0d4446ea265672fe32387","tid":1180110,"uid":54721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T15:08:48.000Z","msg":"下下都屈人唔了解<br />\n個個都係盲巫咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57d381028400601830bc8c56d8f35a11d6518af5","tid":1180110,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T15:45:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img s